Come to think of it, Claudia would also be the vamp. I would LEAST like to encounter, if I suddenly found myself woooooshed (ahhhhh!) into Anne Rice's world as a mortal human being <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     : so she could also snatch the award for 'scariest' vamp. away from Armand as well!<br>
