Scariest &amp; most adorable???? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     Hmmm, I think 'most adorable' if I could see her through preternatural/ vampiric eyes, otherwise, yep .. definititely scariest vampire too!  [She is soooooh angry isn't she .. a woman effectively trapped *forever* in a childs body - so, I guess, who can blame her....you kindof want to be able to put your arms around her &amp; give her a BIG (((hug))) don't you ... probably not a v. gd idea though!]<br>
<br>
I guess this is why Anne Rice is such a good writer: all her characters seem so real &amp; 3-dimensional, they're all complex &amp; they all have personalities (whether they're mortal, vampire, spirit, deity, or whatever).<br>
<br>
Anyway, Pandora is definitely still SEXIEST v.o.a.t., and Lestat still the ultimate v.o.a.t., so at least there's no confusion there...<br>
